Titolo: Kick-Ass 2: The Game

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Kick-Ass 2: The Game is a beat 'em up video game  based on the film Kick-Ass 2. It serves as a sequel to Kick-Ass: The Game. It was developed by Freedom Factory Studios and published by UIG Entertainment. The game was released for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 3, and Xbox 360.The game was heavily criticized by critics, for its technical glitches and lack of originality.